snippet.title: Battlefront+ v10 Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Here's to 7 years of Battlefront II, may there be plenty more to come!
We know it's been a long time and you're all eager to get your hands on BF+ v10 and Kyber v2. While we don't have a release date yet, rest assured that development continues and we're just as excited you are. 

Consider supporting me by donating to my Ko-fi! https://ko-fi.com/thespartancv

Join our Discord to keep up to date on Battlefront Plus and hang out with the devs! https://discord.gg/99VtTgFBqq

You can find Battlefront+ at the following link:
https://www.nexusmods.com/starwarsbattlefront22017/mods/7592
